name: Session 1
description: This session's topic is on Animal Kingdom and the primary focus for this session will be on animal extinction.

name: Session 2
description: This is a continuation from Session 1's topic on Animal Kingdom but the primary focus will be on aquatic mammals

name: Session 3
description: This session's topic is on Forests and the primary focus for this session will be on the importance of forests.

name: Session 4
description: This session's topic is on Data Website and for this session, students will be given hands-on experience on the use of Tableau for data visualisation.

name: Session 5
description: This is a continuation from Session 4's topic on Data Website but the students will now be moving on to more advanced data visualisation tools such as Python.
